[5805]={
["D"]="Welcome to the World of Warcraft!$B$BAs special thanks for purchasing the World of Warcraft Collector\'s Edition, turn in this gift voucher to Merissa Stilwell in Northshire Valley.You\'ll then be given a gift: a little companion to join you on your quest for adventure and glory.$B$BThanks again, and enjoy your stay in the World of Warcraft!$B",
